{"tid":1165164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BU宿生quit hall日 粗口鬧女職員","createTime":"2019-05-21T15:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T15:45:26.000Z","uid":188773,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d25a76d40386beb97fcaf0c6e9b3d1b2cb991dcf","tid":1165164,"uid":188773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"「好X難食，X你老X&hellip;.幾十蚊畀啲屎我哋食！」今早9時許，浸會大學學生宿舍飯堂「浸大食坊」內，有十多名懷疑浸大學生，在飯堂內不停爆粗叫囂，大罵食物難吃，有人更將餐具掉在地上發洩。有飯堂女職員好言相勸，但學生們並沒有收歛，反而連珠爆發粗口，嬉皮笑臉，在場食客為之側目。目擊者斥學生態度無禮兼有辱浸大名聲，已即場用手機拍下影片及向校方投訴。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該批學生部份人是住蔡元培堂宿舍的浸大宿生，今日是QUIT HALL日(即係學期最後住宿舍的一天)，疑有人「離校」在即，趁機發洩對學校餐廳不滿。浸大發言人表示，大學十分關注學生的行為和操守，學生事務處正了解事件，如發現有學生違規，將依據既定程序跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190521/59626374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F59626374&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TUBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=e2782b97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F59626374&h=6344dda2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190521/59626374</a>"},{"pid":"b558d57589e7903d5f34c943aaac9c6a75745b59","tid":1165164,"uid":188773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"有無人識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫BU上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5188219287e88b0e734714b3a9223355b99fb27b","tid":1165164,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:14:39.000Z","msg":"浸大發言人表示嗰段野係咪照抄差佬啲講稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ad34b3bfcdfb051427f11328c739ef91a200bb","tid":1165164,"uid":16844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:15:52.000Z","msg":"橙色多雞"},{"pid":"87a8a86027cf0e